   <taskbody>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Hover over the <image placement="inline"
                      width="20"
                      href="../attachments/45220124/49086829.png"
                      id="image_obk_csn_12c"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
               <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Document</uicontrol> button and select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Fields</uicontrol>
               to open the Document Panel.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         width="278"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/49086830.png"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
               <p class="- topic/p ">All fields are displayed in a list in the order they appear in the document.
                  Current (document), previous (as of last check-in), and current Salesforce values
                  are displayed.</p>
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/49086833.png"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click on a field in the list to snap to and highlight the field in the document.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To change the current value of a field, place your cursor in the field content control in the document and make changes.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="150"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/49086834.png"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Validate</uicontrol> to confirm that the new field value is valid
               for its corresponding data type. </cmd>
            <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">The screen refreshes and displays the message "All fields are valid" if all fields
                  in the document are currently valid. The "Current" value of the field you changed
                  is updated in the list to reflect the change you made.</p>
               <fig id="fig_zxt_d3q_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         width="528"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/49086835.png"
                         id="image_ayt_d3q_12c"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
               <p class="- topic/p ">Changed field values are updated on in the agreement document upon check-in. If
                  you choose to reconcile fields during check-in, they will also be changed on the
                  agreement record.</p>
            </stepresult>
         </step>
      </steps>
